alo, New York|Buffalo, NY]]\n|event    = [[Night of Champions (2011)|Night of Champions]]\n|ref      = <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/inside/titlehistory/wwechampionship/25034698 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110924204856/http://www.wwe.com/inside/titlehistory/wwechampionship/25034698 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2011-09-24 |title=John Cena's tenth reign |accessdate=2011-09-19 |publisher=[[WWE]] }}</ref>\n}}{{PWtitlereign\n|number   = 109\n|champion = {{sortname|Alberto|Del Rio}}\n|reign    = 2\n|date     = {{dts|October 2, 2011}}\n|days     = {{age in days nts|October 2, 2011|November 20, 2011}}\n|days2    = yes\n|location = [[New Orleans|New Orleans, LA]]\n|event    = [[Hell in a Cell (2011)|Hell in a Cell]]\n|notes    = This was a [[Professional wrestling match types#Basic non-elimination matches|triple threat]] [[Hell in a Cell]] match also involving [[CM Punk]].\n|ref      = <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/inside/titlehistory/wwechampionship/25037082 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006141131/http://www.wwe.com/inside/titlehistory/wwechampionship/25037082 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2011-10-06 |title=Alberto Del Rio's second reign |accessdate=2011-10-03 |publisher=[[WWE]] }}</ref>\n}}{{PWtitlereign\n|number   = 110\n|champion = {{sortname|CM|Punk}}\n|reign    = 2\n|date     = {{dts|November 20, 2011}}\n|days     = {{age in days nts|November 20, 2011|January 27, 2013}}\n|days2    = yes\n|location = [[New York City|New York City, NY]]\n|event    = [[Survivor Series (2011)|Survivor Series]]\n|notes    = <!-- PLEASE DO NOT ADD \"LONGEST REIGN OF THE MODERN ERA\" OR ANY VARIATION. This is not essential to this list.-->\n|ref      = <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/inside/titlehistory/wwechampionship/25045682 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124023916/http://www.wwe.com/inside/titlehistory/wwechampionship/25045682 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2011-11-24 |title=CM Punk's second reign |accessdate=2012-0