table-list format, see ''[[List of Portsmouth F.C. players]]''.\n\n===Retired and reserved numbers===\n* Number '''1''' was temporarily retired for the 2001\u201302 season in respect to goalkeeper [[Aaron Flahavan]], who died in a car crash in August 2001, days after being handed the squad number 1 for the first time. Since the 2003\u201304 season, number '''13''' shirt was reserved in respect for him, as this was the number he wore for the majority of his stay at the club.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portsmouth.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=165298|title=There's only one No.13|work=VitalFootball.co.uk |author=Chix |date=10 August 2009 |accessdate=18 January 2019}}</ref> Ten years after his death, however, the number 13 was again used, first by [[Stephen Henderson (footballer, born 1988)|Stephen Henderson]], then by [[Simon Eastwood]], [[Johannes Ertl|Johnny Ertl]] and [[James Bolton (footballer)|James Bolton]] respectively.\n* Number '''12''' is reserved for the [[Fan (person)|fans]] (often referred to as the 12th man).{{citation needed|date=October 2010}}\n* Number '''58''' is \"Nelson\" the club mascot's number.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/pompeynelson?lang=en |title=Nelson/58 |work=twitter.com |accessdate=18 January 2019 }}</ref>\n\n===Portsmouth Player of the Season (since 1968)===\nSource:?{{citation needed|date=June 2019}}\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-4}}\n* 1968 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Ray Pointer]]\n* 1969 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[John Milkins]]\n* 1970 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Nicky Jennings]]\n* 1971 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[David Munks]]\n* 1972 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Richie Reynolds]]\n* 1973 \u2013 N/A\n* 1974 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Paul Went]]\n* 1975 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Mick Mellows]]\n* 1976 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Paul Cahill (English footballer)|Paul Cahill]]\n* 1977 \u2013 N/A\n* 1978 \u2013 N/A\n* 1979 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Peter Mellor]]\n* 1980 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Joe Laidlaw]]\n{{col-4}}\n* 1981 \u2013 N/A\n* 1982 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Alan Knight (footballer)|Alan Knight]]\n* 1983 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Alan Biley]]\n* 1984 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Mark Hateley]]\n* 1985 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Neil Webb]]\n* 1986 \u2013 {{flagicon|Jamaica}} [[Noel Blake]]\n* 1987 \u2013 {{flagicon|Jamaica}} [[Noel Blake]]\n* 1988 \u2013 {{flagicon|Wales}} [[Barry Horne (footballer)|Barry Horne]]\n* 1989 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Micky Quinn]]\n* 1990 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Guy Whittingham]]\n* 1991 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Martin Kuhl]]\n* 1992 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Darren Anderton]]\n* 1993 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Paul Walsh]]\n{{col-4}}\n* 1994 \u2013 {{flagicon|Wales}} [[Kit Symons]]\n* 1995 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Alan Knight (footballer)|Alan Knight]]\n* 1996 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Alan Knight (footballer)|Alan Knight]]\n* 1997 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Lee Bradbury]]\n* 1998 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Andy Awford]]\n* 1999 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Steve Claridge]]\n* 2000 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Steve Claridge]]\n* 2001 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Scott Hiley]]\n* 2002 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Peter Crouch]]\n* 2003 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Linvoy Primus]]\n* 2004 \u2013 {{flagicon|Netherlands}} [[Arjan de Zeeuw]]\n* 2005 \u2013 {{flagicon|Serbia and Montenegro}} [[Dejan Stefanovi\u0107]]\n* 2006 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Gary O'Neil]]\n{{col-4}}\n* 2007 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[David James (footballer, born 1970)|David James]]\n* 2008 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[David James (footballer, born 1970)|David James]]\n* 2009 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Glen Johnson]]\n* 2010 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Jamie O'Hara (footballer)|Jamie O'Hara]]\n* 2011 \u2013 {{flagicon|England}} [[Hayden Mullins]]\n* 2012 \u2013 {{flagicon|Portugal}} [[Ricardo Rocha (footballer, born 1978)|Ricardo Rocha]]\n* 2013 \u2013 {{flagicon|Austria}} [[Jo