thew Clarke (footballer, born 1996)|Matt Clarke]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Portsmouth Hall of Fame===\nPortsmouth created a Hall of Fame in March 2009, which honours former players and staff members of the club.<ref name=\"Hall\">{{cite web|url=http://www.portsmouthfc.co.uk/news/article/hall-of-fame-five-more-inductees-1197989.aspx |title=Hall of Fame: Five More Inductees|publisher=Portsmouth F.C.|date=27 November 2013|accessdate=2 December 2013}}</ref> At a year-by-year ceremony, the club holds a day to announce the year's inducted to the list, and also has a dinner for the people present.\n\nThe following players have been inducted into the Portsmouth Football Club Hall of Fame:\n\n<small>''All appearances and goals according to Soccerbase. * Denotes player for Portsmouth FC Women''</small>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!Inducted!!Name!!Nat.!!Position<br />or role!!Playing career!!Managerial<br />career!!Player<br />Apps!!Player<br />Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|2009<ref>[http://fansonline.net/portsmouth/article.php?id=726 Pompey launch their player Hall of Fame. Who is in it?]; Fans Online, 3 March 2009</ref>||align=\"left\"|[[Jimmy Dickinson]]||{{flagicon|ENG}}||[[Leftwingback|LH]]||1946\u201365||1977\u201379||828||10\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Peter Harris (footballer)|Peter Harris]]||{{flagicon|ENG}}||[[Outside forward|OF]]||1946\u201360||\u2014||515||211\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Ray Hiron]]||{{flagicon|ENG}}||[[Forward (association football)|FW]]||1964\u201375||\u2014||364||117\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Alan Knight (footballer)|Alan Knight]]||{{flagicon|ENG}}||[[Goalkeeper (association football)|GK]]||1978\u20132000/2003\u201304||\u2014||801||0\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Guy Whittingham]]||{{flagicon|ENG}}||[[Striker (association football)|ST]]||1992\u201394||2012\u201313||249||112\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|2010<ref>[http://www.portsmouth.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=185870 Hall of Fame 2010 dinner info]; Vital Football, 25 January 2010</ref>||align=\